- Adds the ability to create and run shell commands from the web interface (resolves #75, #84)

  ![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/447801/21578204/4c83189e-cfb2-11e6-962c-cc7aaf633649.png)

  See an example [.cncrc](https://github.com/cheton/cnc/blob/master/examples/.cncrc.example) file:

  ``` json
  {
    "watchDirectory": "/path/to/dir",
    "accessTokenLifetime": "30d",
    "allowRemoteAccess": false,
    "state": {
      "checkForUpdates": true
    },
    "commands": [
      {
        "text": "Check network connection",
        "command": "ping -c 10 127.0.0.1"
      },
      {
        "text": "Reboot",
        "command": "sudo /sbin/reboot"
      },
      {
        "text": "Shutdown",
        "command": "sudo /sbin/shutdown"
      }
    ],
    "macros": [],
    "users": []
  }
  ```
